! Gruvbox-inspired colour scheme for the X Window System
! Original gruvbox theme: https://github.com/morhetz/gruvbox

! Common colours

#define C_yellow        #d79921
#define C_orange        #d65d0e
#define C_red           #cc241d
#define C_magenta       #b16286
#define C_violet        #6c71c4
#define C_blue          #458588
#define C_cyan          #689d6a
#define C_green         #98971a

! Theme

*background:              C_background
*foreground:              C_foreground
*fadeColor:               C_background
*cursorColor:             C_cursor
*pointerColorBackground:  C_pointer_bg
*pointerColorForeground:  C_cursor

*color0:                  C_base0
*color1:                  C_red
*color2:                  C_green
*color3:                  C_yellow
*color4:                  C_blue
